b_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/563840/extras/cfe3de674eb9bdf86cf97df0607044bc.avif?t=1762795930\" width=600 height=76 /></span><br><br>Ultimately, you'll discover a tale of loyalty, despair, and betrayal, as echoes of the lost Yanrana culture come to life in a lush wilderness devoid of man.",
